{"tid":441373,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"買牛熊證真係學好多野","createTime":"2017-10-19T14:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T09:48:23.000Z","uid":145959,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"bd8d2d2da31cd143fa36cf98acf9fe8f7117428d","tid":441373,"uid":145959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:55:39.000Z","msg":"我自己每次玩都用好少本而且買得勁貼<br />\n可以我每次買每隻都只買十萬股<br />\n-見住佢跌又會好後悔入手<br />\n-見住佢爆又會自滿<br />\n-爆少少嗰陣想入多啲貨等佢爆，點知事與願違，一追就仆街了，唔追就仲有賺<br />\n-有賺少少就早左放，點知之後爆上去，自己又Dum心口<br />\n-知個巿今日跌，但比佢抽一抽嚇到我走都走唔切<br />\n-明明0.017係你面前，但自己叫限價盤0.016，等佢去到0.030先死死氣氣入手因為知唔入就太遲。搞到因小失大<br />\n<br />\n所以話玩牛熊證真係好考心理質素<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 9up"},{"pid":"f420fa61576f22d8c1f0bee5eb9ff61274cb7b2c","tid":441373,"uid":145959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95250e885cd0f8508e59e350069458c80c42564","tid":441373,"uid":86756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:17:08.000Z","msg":"熊仔琴日平手走，今日見到佢升3倍幾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9720266378d9b4cab810ad1be7ab1a23db6bc0","tid":441373,"uid":46640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:19:20.000Z","msg":"新手同樣有咁問題，贏少少輸鋪勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f33302cb45db69687bf281cc625a3fc13940a52","tid":441373,"uid":64131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:22:06.000Z","msg":"玩角球算"},{"pid":"9ee3f3a8ea8f82925ddf96e0eeaf13f46ed12aa0","tid":441373,"uid":145959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手同樣有咁問題，贏少少輸鋪勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgm