 class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 110都啪左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a06dafb362aadd697473f15e7e3593c6fcada1","tid":441373,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:44:08.000Z","msg":"點解唔玩期權"},{"pid":"6aa89dafd4b4d08a31338dc69ddf763f1200fe8d","tid":441373,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔玩期權</blockquote><br />\n唔係隻隻有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea849ed5d0679e18b66e6dd7ed6a38bfbfeba832","tid":441373,"uid":145959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新手同樣有咁問題，贏少少輸鋪勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我而家專攻仙熊，玩裂口位<br />\n<br />\n本唔好放太多，因為你輸唔起。買少少輸曬冇所謂呢種心態贏面多啲，因為你有耐性等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買打靶牛熊心理質素真係要好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 大時代之前打番個和就&rdquo;介&rdquo;左牛熊，自問心理質素唔好成日睇住個市，搞到神經緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我係新手，我由9月開始有得開巿就會買牛熊，頭一個月係心理質素勁差，見佢跌0.001已經想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後尾不斷調整調整。<br />\n到左琴日買左5000 28800熊，後尾見到夜期同美巿咁已經淆曬，嗰刻我先知我仲係一個心理狀態好差嘅炒家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由開巿差幾點打靶，不停講等啊等啊等啊。見距離拉遠左入多10萬股，下就2隻都翻左幾倍。"},{"pid":"178b59372e95454a06ecc01c4b1291403d786355","tid":441373,"uid":145959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:49:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔玩期權</blockquote><br />\n巴打我都想學，呢個點入手？我上網見過二元期權，係咪同呢個又兩樣野嚟？我冇研究過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5c171370c4f6394f628ea94