faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abddcbf8d58df020ff0c2cc451558bec2b68fd4b","tid":441373,"uid":89256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:43:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇完d留言，發覺好多人搞唔清牛熊，輪，期權同期貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n牛熊係期貨，理論上無時間值<br />\n輪係期權，有時間值<br />\n港交所有股票期權同期貨買賣<br />\n<br />\n想知咩可以係下面問<br />\n<br />\n利伸: UST fina grad<br />\n做左幾年經紀，見盡d客輸到仆街</blockquote><br />\n點輸法？</blockquote><br />\n幾球幾球咁輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我算有良心，會勸下d客，唔好玩呢d，因為太大風險<br />\n佢唔聽都無計"},{"pid":"7a4b17170852f66cf0219b4cc1daa54dce333732","tid":441373,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:43:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解唔玩期權</blockquote><br />\n巴打我都想學，呢個點入手？我上網見過二元期權，係咪同呢個又兩樣野嚟？我冇研究過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n二元期權係賭大細<br />\n期權係另一樣野黎 類似期指</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我Google下先，其實期權交易係咪快過牛熊？</blockquote><br />\n何謂快過牛熊<br />\n牛熊有莊家 保證下接貨力<br />\n期權唔一定有莊家 論理上你自己都可以做莊 但太價外或者遠期既唔一定有人接貨</blockquote><br />\n其實期權都有莊家，佢地有責任出價<br />\n如果太價外無人出價，可以打電話叫佢地出價<br />\n不過班仆街出價會mar到勁闊，同埋出30秒左右就會取消番個盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你期權如果不貪心，做好哂保護，基本上不會輸好多"},{"pid":"d152a9cf958f48705f2da82a66308c3952ed9dba","tid":441373,"uid":89256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解唔玩期權</blockquote><br />\n巴打我都想學，呢個點入手？我上網見過二元期權，係咪同呢個又兩樣野嚟？我冇研究過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br /